RatingDim_1.label: RatingDim_1
RatingDim_1.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.SurveyQuestionResponsewithDetails_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'Question_QuestionType' in ["Rating"];rating = group q by ('Id', 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', 'QuestionChoices_Name');rating = foreach rating generate 'Id' , 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', 'QuestionChoices_Name' as 'QuestionChoices_Name', first('CreatedDate_sec_epoch') as 'CreatedDate_sec_epoch',  first('NumberValue') as 'NumberValue', first('RatingDim') as 'RatingDim';rating = order rating by ('SurveyVersion_Survey_Id' asc, 'SurveyVersionId' asc, 'QuestionId' asc, 'QuestionChoices_Name' asc);rating = group rating by ('Id', 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId');rating = foreach rating generate 'Id' , 'SurveyVersion_Survey_Id', 'SurveyVersionId', 'QuestionId', first('NumberValue')/string_to_number(last('QuestionChoices_Name')) * 5 as 'Rating',first('RatingDim') as 'RatingDim';final_output = group rating by ('RatingDim');final_output = foreach final_output generate 'RatingDim' as 'RatingDim', {{cell(Toggle_1.selection, 0, "mea_rating").asString()}};final_output = order final_output by 'RatingDim' asc;

values.mea_rating: count(rating) as 'Responses';final_output = group final_output by 'RatingDim';final_output = foreach final_output generate 'RatingDim', (sum('Responses')/sum(sum('Responses')) over ([..] partition by all))*100 as '% of Responses'
values.mea_rating2: count(q) as 'Responses';q = group q by 'RatingDim';q = foreach q generate 'RatingDim', (sum('Responses')/sum(sum('Responses')) over ([..] partition by all))*100 as '% of Responses'

RatingDim_Score.label: RatingDim_Score
RatingDim_Score.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.SurveyQuestionResponsewithDetails_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by 'Question_QuestionType' == "CSAT";q = group q by 'RatingDim';q = foreach q generate 'RatingDim' as 'RatingDim', {{cell(Toggle_1.selection, 0, "mea_rating2").asString()}};q = order q by 'RatingDim' asc;q = limit q 2000;
